&lt;p&gt;A handheld game console programmable with (Micro/Circuit)Python.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="project-thumb"&gt;
&lt;a class="reference external image-reference" href="/_images/4787691512171711474.jpg"&gt;&lt;img alt="projects/project-27629/images/4787691512171711474.jpg" src="projects/project-27629/images/4787691512171711474.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a class="reference external image-reference" href="/_images/5532001510259340085.jpg"&gt;&lt;img alt="projects/project-27629/images/5532001510259340085.jpg" src="projects/project-27629/images/5532001510259340085.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a class="reference external image-reference" href="/_images/5854921525097630407.jpg"&gt;&lt;img alt="projects/project-27629/images/5854921525097630407.jpg" src="projects/project-27629/images/5854921525097630407.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
